;
; MFA XP MQB Label file. Valid for software V1.06 and above
;
; (C) MFA XP Automotive Systems 2019
;
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
; Long Coding
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
;
; {Basic Setup}
LC,00,0~1,00,Language: German
LC,00,0~1,01,Language: English
LC,00,2,Show raw boost pressure instead of height corrected
LC,00,3,External exhaust temperature sensor installed
LC,00,4,External oil pressure sensor installed
; {Externer boost pressure sensor}
LC,00,5~6,00,External boost pressure sensor: Not installed
LC,00,5~6,20,External boost pressure sensor: VW 250kPA
LC,00,5~6,40,External boost pressure sensor: VW 300kPA
LC,00,5~6,60,External boost pressure sensor: VW 400kPA
; {Workshop mode}
LC,00,7,Workshop mode (MFA XP not visible)
; {Units Setup}
LC,01,0,Temperature Unit: 蚌 instead of 蚓
LC,01,1,Speed Unit: MPH instead of KM/H
LC,01,2,Power Unit: KW instead of HP
LC,01,3,Torque Unit: LBF instead of NM
LC,01,4,Pressure Unit: PSI instead of BAR
LC,01,5,Signal source of Car Speed is ABS/ESP instead of instrument cluster
LC,01,6,Adapt signal Car Speed with fast reading
; {Exhaust Flap}
LC,02,0~1,00,Control both flaps
LC,02,0~1,01,Control only flap 1
LC,02,0~1,02,Control only flap 2
LC,02,2~4,00,Exhaust flap control deactivated
LC,02,2~4,04,Toggle between open / stock
LC,02,2~4,08,Toggle between closed / stock
LC,02,2~4,0C,Toggle between open / closed
LC,02,2~4,10,Toggle between open / closed / stock
LC,02,5~6,00,Initial flap state (ignition on): Stock
LC,02,5~6,20,Initial flap state (ignition on): Open
LC,02,5~6,40,Initial flap state (ignition on): Closed
LC,02,5~6,60,Initial flap state (ignition on): Last state
LC,02,7,Invert signal logic (for after market flap controls)
; {Display behaviour}
LC,03,0~2,00,No hysteresis, show raw data
LC,03,0~2,01,Apply hysteresis to all values
LC,03,0~2,02,Apply hysteresis to all values except boost pressure
LC,03,4~7,00,Hysteris: Stage 1 (small impact)
LC,03,4~7,10,Hysteris: Stage 2
LC,03,4~7,20,Hysteris: Stage 3
LC,03,4~7,40,Hysteris: Stage 4 (biggest impact)
; {car type}
LC,04,0~2,00,Vehicle type: VW MQB
LC,04,0~2,01,Vehicle type: Audi MQB
LC,04,0~2,02,Vehicle type: Seat MQB
LC,04,0~2,03,Vehicle type: Skoda MQB
LC,04,0~2,04,Vehicle type: Audi TT MQB
